Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booster
    A booster pickup which gives the player heightened speed and jumping ability.
    Boss
    A boss DynamicBody which is present in level 3 and is able to kill the player upon contact.
    Controller
    A class that handles the different inputs for player controls.
    ControlPanel
    A control panel for controls within the game.
    Controls
    A class that shows the player game controls.
    Enemy
    A enemy class that handles enemy bodies.
    Game
    A game class where everything comes together.
    GameLevel
    A game level class that has the generals of all levels.
    GiveFocus
    A mouse listener that gives the keyboard focus to a specified component.
    Heart
    Handles the heart objects in game.
    Key
    handles the key objects in game.
    KillEnemy
    allows the player to kill enemies with projectiles.
    Level1
    initiates Level 1.
    Level2
    initiates Level 2.
    Level3
    initiates Level 3.
    Level4
    initiates Level 4.
    Menu
    Handles the main menu of the game.
    MyView
    Handles the what the user can see the background and foreground.
    Orb
    Handles the orb body that is a projectile.
    Pickup
    Handles all the pickups in the game.
    Player
    Handles the player body and the star health values.
    Portal
    Handles the portal body which enables the player to progress.
    PortalListener
    Allows the player to move to next level upon contact with portal.
    PowerUp  
    Projectile
    handles projectile that can kill enemies.
    Star
    a class that increases the player score upon contact.
    Tracker
    Pan the view to follow a particular body.
